casebody.data:
No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 525 U. S. 805.]

Motion of the River Master for fees and expenses granted, and it is ordered that the River Master is awarded a total of $2,505 for the period January 1 through March 31,1999, to be paid equally by the parties.
